comments: Doncic (DAL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Sabonis (SAC) briefly grasps Williams' (DAL) arm, and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Doncic (DAL) extends both hands forward and initiates contact with Fox (SAC) during the drive, affecting his SQBR.
Lively II (DAL) moves alongside Fox's (SAC) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
The scorer's table inadvertently started the clock without a player making contact with the ball and it was correctly reset to 0:53.1 during DAL's inbound.
Huerter (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position as Hardaway Jr. (DAL) dribbles the ball off of his own foot, causing him to lose control of the ball.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) commits at take foul on Fox (SAC).
Sabonis (SAC) is drawn into the air on the shot fake and initiates contact with Doncic's (DAL) body as he contests the jump shot attempt.
Williams (DAL) brings his arm toward Fox's (SAC) path and marginal contact occurs during Fox's drive.
Green (DAL) initiates contact with Fox's (SAC) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Fox (SAC) takes more than 8 seconds to establish position in the frontcourt.
Williams (DAL) commits a take foul on Monk (SAC).
Williams (DAL) inbounds the ball within 5 seconds
Huerter (SAC) moves alongside Kleber's (DAL) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Kleber (DAL) extends both hands forward and commits a take foul on Fox (SAC).
Doncic (DAL) commits a take foul on Barnes (SAC).
